cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a novel transductive inference framework for metric-based meta-learning models, which is a common topic in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method is applied and validated on four benchmark datasets commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks. The paper also involves meta-learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
